Name: Stillwater
About the game: 'I'll Never Forgive You!' Private Investigator Hugo Laurent was ready to busy himself with more paperwork until a disturbed young woman entered his office to request an investigation regarding her grandfather's safety. What danger awaits underneath the surface of this mystery? Gorgeous and atmospheric artwork by ota and sasa. 7,000~ words and 2 endings. A cute and loyal dog!
